data.title: Birthday Parties
data.meta_description: Built on the idea that every day deserves a little bit of “wow”, Warehouse Cinemas is a new movie theater company offering first-run films, top-notch food and drinks, exceptional picture and sound, and heated leather recliner seating in every auditorium. Find a Warehouse Cinemas movie theater near you and find out that it's more than a movie theater. It’s an experience.
data.text:
ELEVATE YOUR BIRTHDAY PARTY EXPERIENCE

Birthday Party packages are an extension of our Private Movie Screening packages. Please note we do not have party rooms or lobby options for Birthday Parties. Birthday package includes:

Private Auditorium

Decorations, including balloons outside of auditorium w/ special message for birthday guest

Choose from current release movie or retro movie

$2 off discount for snack packs for 10 or more people

6-ft table and tablecloth in the back of the auditorium for cake, supplies, and gift

Plates and forks provided + large plastic serving knife for cake

Access to auditorium is 1 hour prior to the showtime and 5 minutes after the end of the final credits

Available Times: Saturdays and Sundays at 11:30AM. Available on a first-come first-serve basis.
